name: ICES Historical Plankton Dataset
description:
Data from seven historical ICES volumes has been digitized and quality checked through a cooperativeproject between SAHFOS, ICES and the University of Plymouth(UK). Data include >13,000 planktonsamples. Approximately 2000 taxa, many identified to species level, are included. The data are from a variety of cruises. Within EurOBISand EMODnet, presence only values havebeen made available.
